## üõ†Ô∏è Root Cause Handling (Self-Healing)
- **Syntax Guards**: Automatically detect and fix common LLM errors like `unterminated string literals` by checking quote counts.
- **Conflict Cleaning**: Automatically remove Git conflict markers and diff indicators from generated code before applying.
